&lt;div class="mermaid" id="id-1">&lt;/div>&lt;p>Did you know when we ask young kids to share toys, they often cannot fathom why we ask? To them, the toy is theirs, the feeling is obvious, and the rule feels arbitrary.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>